\c 4
\s Iziphathamandla zikaSolomoni
\p
\v 1 Ngakho inkosi uSolomoni yaba yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli wonke.
\v 2 Lalezi yiziphathamandla ayelazo: UAzariya indodana kaZadoki wayengumpristi;
\v 3 uElihorefi loAhiya amadodana kaShisha\x + 2 Sam. 8.17. 20.25. 1 Lan. 18.16.\x* babengababhali; uJehoshafathi indodana kaAhiludi wayengumabhalane;
\v 4 loBhenaya indodana kaJehoyada wayephezu kwebutho\x + 2.35. 2 Sam. 8.18.\x*; loZadoki loAbhiyatha babengabapristi\x + 2.27. 2 Sam. 20.25.\x*;
\v 5 loAzariya indodana kaNathani wayephezu kwabaphathi\x + 4.7,19,27. 5.16. 9.23. 22.47. 2 Lan. 8.10.\x*; uZabudi indodana kaNathani wayengumphathi omkhulu\x + 4.2. 2 Sam. 8.18. 20.26.\x*, umngane wenkosi\x + 2 Sam. 15.37.\x*;
\v 6 loAhishari wayengumlawuli wendlu; loAdoniramu indodana kaAbida wayephezu kwemithelo\x + 12.18. 5.14. 2 Sam. 20.24. 2 Lan. 10.18.\x*.
\p
\v 7 USolomoni wayelabaphathi abalitshumi lambili phezu kukaIsrayeli wonke, ababedingela inkosi lendlu yayo ukudla, ngulowo lalowo ngenyanga yakhe ngomnyaka wadinga ukudla\x + 4.7,19,27. 5.16. 9.23. 22.47. 2 Lan. 8.10.\x*.
\v 8 Lala ngamabizo abo: UBeni-Huri entabeni zakoEfrayimi\x + Josh. 24.33.\x*.
\v 9 UBeni-Dekeri eMakazi leShahalibimi\x + Hlu. 1.35. 2 Sam. 23.32.\x* leBeti-Shemeshi\x + Josh. 19.22,38.\x* leEloni-Beti-Hanani.
\v 10 UBeni-Hesedi eArubothi, eleSoko\x + 1 Sam. 17.1. Josh. 15.35,48.\x* lelizwe lonke leHeferi\x + Josh. 12.17.\x*.
\v 11 UBeni-Abinadaba \add wayele\add*lizwe lonke leDori\x + Josh. 11.2.\x*; uTafathi indodakazi kaSolomoni wayengumkakhe.
\v 12 UBahana indodana kaAhiludi\x + 4.3.\x* \add wayele\add*Thahanakhi\x + Hlu. 5.19.\x* leMegido\x + Hlu. 5.19.\x* layo yonke iBeti-Sheyani\x + Josh. 17.11.\x*, eseceleni kweZarethani\x + Hlu. 7.22.\x* ngaphansi kweJizereyeli\x + Josh. 17.16.\x*, kusukela eBeti-Sheyani\x + Josh. 17.11.\x* kuze kube seAbeli-Mehola\x + Hlu. 7.22.\x*, kuze kube ngaphetsheya kweJokimeyama\x + 1 Lan. 6.68. Josh. 19.11.\x*.
\v 13 UBeni-Geberi eRamothi-Gileyadi\x + 22.3.\x* wayelemizi kaJayiri indodana kaManase, eseGileyadi\x + Nani 32.41.\x*, wayelelizwe leArigobi\x + Dute. 3.4. 2 Lan. 8.5.\x*, eliseBashani, imizi engamatshumi ayisithupha emikhulu elemiduli lemigoqo yethusi\x + Dute. 3.4. 2 Lan. 8.5.\x*.
\v 14 UAhinadaba indodana kaIdo eMahanayimi\x + 1 Lan. 27.21.\x*.
\v 15 UAhimahazi wayekoNafithali\x + 2 Sam. 15.27.\x*; laye wathatha uBasemathi indodakazi kaSolomoni abe ngumka\add khe\add*.
\v 16 UBahana indodana kaHushayi wayekoAsheri leAlothi\x + 2 Sam. 15.37.\x*.
\v 17 UJehoshafathi indodana kaParuwa wayekoIsakari.
\v 18 UShimeyi indodana kaEla wayekoBhenjamini\x + 1.8.\x*.
\v 19 UGeberi indodana kaUri wayeselizweni leGileyadi, ilizwe likaSihoni inkosi yamaAmori, lelikaOgi inkosi yeBashani. Njalo wayenguye yedwa umphathi kulelolizwe\x + Dute. 3.8-10.\x*.
\s Ukuhlakanipha lokuphumelela kukaSolomoni
\p
\v 20 UJuda loIsrayeli babebanengi njengetshebetshebe elingaselwandle ngobunengi, besidla, benatha, bethokoza\x + 4.29. 3.8. Gen. 22.17. 2 Lan. 1.9.\x*.
\v 21 USolomoni wayesebusa phezu kwayo yonke imibuso\x + 2 Lan. 9.26. Hlab. 72.8.\x* kusukela emfuleni \add kuze kufike\add* elizweni lamaFilisti\x + Gen. 15.18.\x* kuze kufike emngceleni weGibhithe; babeletha izipho, babemsebenzela uSolomoni zonke izinsuku zempilo yakhe\x + Hlab. 72.10. 1 Sam. 10.27.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Njalo ukudla kukaSolomoni ngosuku olulodwa \w kwakungamakhori\w** angamatshumi amathathu empuphu ecolekileyo, lamakori angamatshumi ayisithupha empuphu,
\v 23 inkabi ezilitshumi ezinonisiweyo, lenkabi ezingamatshumi amabili zemadlelweni, lezimvu ezilikhulu, ngaphandle kwendluzele\x + Dute. 12.15.\x*, lemiziki\x + Dute. 12.15.\x*, lemiziki elempondo ezilembaxambaxa\x + Dute. 14.5.\x*, lenyoni ezinonisiweyo.
\v 24 Ngoba wayebusa phezu kwalo lonke nganeno komfula, kusukela eTifisa\x + 2 Kho. 15.16.\x* kusiya eGaza\x + Gen. 10.19. Josh. 15.47.\x*, laphezu kwawo wonke amakhosi nganeno komfula, njalo wayelokuthula kuzo zonke inhlangothi zakhe ezizingelezeleyo\x + 1 Lan. 22.9.\x*.
\v 25 UJuda loIsrayeli bahlala-ke bevikelekile, ngulowo lalowo ngaphansi kwesivini sakhe\x + Mika 4.4. 2 Kho. 18.31. Isa. 36.16. Zek. 3.10.\x* langaphansi komkhiwa wakhe, kusukela koDani kuze kufike eBherishebha, zonke izinsuku zikaSolomoni\x + 2 Sam. 3.10.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Njalo uSolomoni wayelezindlwana zamabhiza enqola zakhe ezizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane, labagadi bamabhiza abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili\x + 10.26. 2 Lan. 1.14. 2 Lan. 9.25. Dute. 17.16.\x*.
\v 27 Lalabobaphathi badingela inkosi uSolomoni ukudla, laye wonke osondela etafuleni lenkosi uSolomoni, ngulowo lalowo ngenyanga yakhe; kabatshiyanga kusweleke lutho\x + 4.5.\x*.
\v 28 \w Lebhali\w** lamahlanga awamabhiza lawamabhiza alejubane bakuletha endaweni lapho \add eyayifanele\add* kube khona, ngulowo lalowo njengemfanelo yakhe.
\p
\v 29 UNkulunkulu wasemnika uSolomoni inhlakanipho lokuqedisisa okukhulu kakhulu\x + 3.12.\x*, lobubanzi benhliziyo, njengetshebetshebe elisekhunjini lolwandle\x + 4.20.\x*.
\v 30 Lenhlakanipho kaSolomoni yayinkulu kulenhlakanipho yawo wonke amadodana empumalanga\x + Hlu. 6.3.\x*, lakulenhlakanipho yonke yeGibhithe\x + Seb. 7.22. Isa. 19.11.\x*.
\v 31 Ngoba wayehlakaniphile kulabo bonke abantu\x + 3.12.\x*, okwedlula uEthani\x + 1 Lan. 6.44. 15.17,19. Hlab. 89.\x* umEzira\x + 1 Lan. 2.6.\x* loHemani\x + 1 Lan. 2.6. 1 Lan. 6.33. 15.17,19. 25.1,4,5,6. Hlab. 88.\x* loKalikoli\x + 1 Lan. 2.6.\x* loDarida amadodana kaMaholi; lebizo lakhe lalisezizweni zonke inhlangothi zonke.
\v 32 Waseqamba izaga ezizinkulungwane ezintathu\x + Zaga 1.1. Tshu. 12.9.\x*, lengoma zakhe zaziyinkulungwane lanhlanu.
\v 33 Wasekhuluma ngezihlahla, kusukela esihlahleni somsedari oseLebhanoni\x + Hlu. 9.15.\x* kuze kufike \w kuhisope\w** emila iphuma emdulini\x + Eks. 12.22.\x*; wakhuluma langezinyamazana langezinyoni langezihuquzelayo langezinhlanzi.
\v 34 Kwasekufika abavela ezizweni zonke ukuzwa inhlakanipho kaSolomoni, bevela emakhosini wonke omhlaba ayezwe ngenhlakanipho yakhe\x + 10.1. 2 Lan. 9.23.\x*.
